{"tid":1294380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解無人搞公園靜坐（和理非入）","createTime":"2019-07-07T18:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T19:00:39.000Z","uid":219693,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e600b1ebe1b7129a15992c07418e2ae31e477b","tid":1294380,"uid":219693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:39:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">發夢見到有篇咁嘅嘢所以打出嚟<br />\n內容是咁的</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">靜坐又可以吸納多啲和理非<br />\n喺公園搞又唔會比警察清埸<br />\n靜坐一個月左右政府應該會有人出嚟<br />\n<br />\n平日學生、師奶、阿公阿婆可以出嚟坐下<br />\n六日啲人放假/工又可以出嚟<br />\n又唔會搞到民生（翻工人士唔會屌）<br />\n又唔會搞到警察（撐警人士屌唔到）<br />\n又唔㑹有破壞（保皇黨屌唔到）<br />\n可以比啲唔想衝嘅人參加<br />\n<br />\n理想地點：維園（有冇其他提議）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個人認為可以令整運動提升層次 變更高尚更長久更多人支持</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後一句香港人加油</span>"},{"pid":"95b110375c491fe2b52addb1f97328cb27ecef5f","tid":1294380,"uid":93998,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:40:18.000Z","msg":"睇下今日幾和平<br />\n咪一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d1ad7bdc47449b68350cfb2cb71c149323d883","tid":1294380,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:41:13.000Z","msg":"靜坐一個月左右政府應該會有人出嚟<br />\n<br />\n你搞緊笑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fac4bf71f187f70046b2af146fae72f384ed41b","tid":1294380,"uid":180168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:41:19.000Z","msg":"有次咪集完會<br />\n3條友走出黎叫人圍警總<br />\n跟住咪成大班跟住去"},{"pid":"f79037c93b5dd599760464d6ec3895231ec52e6e","tid":1294380,"uid":180168,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"95b110375c491fe2b52addb1f97328cb27ecef5f","tid":1294380,"uid":93998,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:40:18.000Z","msg":"睇下今日幾和平<br />\n咪一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"